== Deaths == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1567]] {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}） – {{ill|Takeda Yoshinobu|ja|武田義信|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander ({{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (born {{ill|1538|de|1538|ja|1538|zh|1538|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).
