== Events == * {{ill|Emperor Tenji|ja|天智天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[671]] {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}） – {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|大海人皇子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was entrusted with state affairs by {{ill|Emperor Tenji|ja|天智天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, but he refused the responsibility and took monastic vows at Yoshino. * {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1679]] {{ill|November 22|ja|11月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}） – The succession dispute and disturbance in {{ill|Takada Domain|ja|高田藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was adjudicated by the {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|徳川幕府|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} Tairō – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi|ja|酒井忠清|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} – with the faction opposed to {{ill|Oguri Masamasa|ja|小栗美作|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (the hereditary retainer) being placed under another house’s custody.
== Births == * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1624]] {{ill|November 29|ja|11月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}） – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi|ja|酒井忠清|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, an early Edo period hereditary daimyō, rōjū, and tairō (died [[1681]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1567]] {{ill|November 19|ja|11月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}） – {{ill|Takeda Yoshinobu|ja|武田義信|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander ({{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (born {{ill|1538|de|1538|ja|1538|zh|1538|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).
